{"tid":1256063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉指示威者交稅少 質疑為何圍稅局","createTime":"2019-06-24T20:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T02:10:55.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2a842edde1e05b00dfc13ecd5ee34f83e5d772","tid":1256063,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T20:58:27.000Z","msg":"有網民不滿政府未回應反修例人士訴求，發動「接放工」行動癱瘓政府運作，一度約有200名示威人士聚集稅務大樓大堂。身兼行政會議成員的新民黨葉劉淑儀表示，這些年輕人交稅不多，質疑為何要包圍稅務局。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀又指出，除衝擊警總、入境處，現在又包圍稅務局，認為示威者的訴求似乎已跟修例沒有關係，政府就算再退一步、改字眼，短期內都難以平息，反而引發新一輪訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2171500/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2171500%2F&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443sorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=d95e5dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2171500/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f4e3f68a3d5b16ff1e34301658e5f0b85cdf77","tid":1256063,"uid":264299,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T20:59:14.000Z","msg":"佢出少句聲會唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff74e58a73bfcba113c2714ec1c946dbcc7313a","tid":1256063,"uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10f4e3f68a3d5b16ff1e34301658e5f0b85cdf77","tid":1256063,"uid":264299,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T20:59:14.000Z","msg":"佢出少句聲會唔會死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T21:00:18.000Z","msg":"俾人串鳩<br />\n冇聲出咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c030d829e317f713a6a32df4f0fc9404ab604c2","tid":1256063,"uid":20058,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T21